entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've completed all of the test races and claimed your prize. Head back to Watto and give him the droid motivator.
entries.journal_entry_description: An'Kwee wants you to prove you're a speeder pilot before she will help you find the droid motivator.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: An'Kwee wants you to talk to Draknus about running some races as a test for An'Kwee.
